'''UDMFConvert''' is a utility written by Brendon Duncan to convert binary-format maps to [[UDMF]]. It is published under the terms of the GNU GPL v3, and the source code is included along with three win32 binary files in the distribution.
== External links == * [https://github.com/CO2/UDMF-Convert UDMF Convert] on GitHub
[[Category:Map converters]][[Category:UDMF]]
